cmp.com/news/china/science/article/3213788/chinas-overseas-coal-exit-fuelled-bottom-line-not-green-leadership-experts-say?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3221586_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="2d492764-2c00-4fac-b8fa-06c1fdb88e09" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-bundle="article">从煤</a>中提取低碳化合物的生产方面取得了重大进展，这可能会产生可观的经济效益，并对国家的<a href="https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3220788/how-energy-powering-chinas-relationships-central-asia?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3221586_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="bd1f44ac-5aea-4bf9-8018-6d3d8dad3409" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-bundle="article">能源和资源</a>安全产生深远影响。</p><p>该研究集中在烯烃——也称为烯烃——一类化合物，作为生产各种工业产品的重要原材料，如塑料、药品、化妆品，甚至航天器。 </p><div class="meter__linear relative" id="default-meter-page-views-11"><img width="auto" height="1" src="https://www.scmp.com/images/1x1.png" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="dm__l3"><hr class="vertical-line"><div class="dm__lw"><svg class="dm__l" height="24" viewBox="0 0 18 24" width="18" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><g style="stroke:#000;fill:none;fill-rule:evenodd;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-width:1.5"><rect height="13.5" rx="1.5" width="16.5" x=".75" y="9.75"></rect><path d="m3.75 9.75v-3.75c0-2.89949494 2.35050506-5.25 5.25-5.25 2.8994949 0 5.25 2.35050506 5.25 5.25v3.75"></path><path d="m9.00000067 15.75c-.20710745 0-.37500067.1678932-.37500067.3749993 0 .2071075.16789322.3750007.37500067.3750007.20710611 0 .37499933-.1678932.37499933-.3750007.0002665-.0995369-.03915673-.1950746-.10954072-.2654586-.070384-.070384-.16592164-.1098072-.26545861-.1095407z"></path></g></svg></div></div><div class="dm__b center-block"><div><div class="dm__h mb-16">您已达到免费文章数量限制。</div><div class="dm__t center-block">订阅 SCMP 以无限制地访问我们屡获殊荣的新闻</div><div class="dm__s2 mt-30"><div class="dm__sb" id="subscribe-btn-11-large" role="button" tabindex="0" sub